# Bug Management

When creating or updating bugs:

- Use `ai-framework/templates/bug.template.yaml`
- ID format: BUG-XXXX in `Test/{{AREA}}/bugs/`
- Include steps to reproduce, expected vs actual
- Link to REQ and TC when applicable
- Add failing test before fix when feasible

See `ai-framework/agents/bug-manager.md` and `workflows/bug-fix.workflow.md`.
